headline.print_headline: Yemen's AQAP Calls on Islamists to Target America After Iraq Air Strikes
headline.main: Yemen's AQAP Calls on Islamists to Target America After Iraq Air Strikes

lead_paragraph: Al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula, one of the group's deadliest franchises, called on Islamists to target the United States, after Washington launched air strikes in Iraq against Islamist militants who operate as the Islamic State.
